er":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"9話、42話、44話、51話：りずむとヒビキの秘密の場所。という割には人通りが多くオープンなのですが（笑）。48話で判明しますが、りずむパパがママにプロポーズしたという、親子二代に渡って大事な所なのです","density":15,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.445962%2C139.650364"},{"id":"ko2dmcas9","geo":[35.446021,139.650245],"priority":26,"name":"山下公園：阿世知社長の思い","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"25話：りずむのオーロラライジングへの無謀な挑戦を見た社長は、そなたとオーロラライジングの事を思い起こす…","density":15,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.446021%2C139.650245"},{"id":"ko2dmca7f","geo":[35.447196,139.648092],"priority":15,"name":"山下公園：赤い靴はいてた女の子の像（DMF）","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"44話：オーロラドリーム、ディアマイフューチャーのヒロイン達が全員集合","density":272,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.447196%2C139.648092"},{"id":"ko2dmcax2","geo":[35.4523,139.642222],"priority":13,"name":"赤レンガ倉庫：みおん様の撮影現場","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"14話：プロ意識とは言っても投げ捨てるのはどうかと思いますよ、みおん様…。この回のみおん様は前歯がかわいい（笑）","density":48,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.4523%2C139.642222"},{"id":"ko2dmcamx","geo":[35.452197,139.642638],"priority":7,"name":"赤レンガ倉庫：ハロウィン","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"30話：ハロウィンエピソード全般。ショウさん…","density":31,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.452197%2C139.642638"},{"id":"ko2dmcajq","geo":[35.452295,139.642898],"priority":13,"name":"赤レンガ倉庫","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"4話：外車に乗ったおじさんがJCをナンパ！？","density":31,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.452295%2C139.642898"},{"id":"ko2dmcaoc","geo":[35.45816,139.636196],"priority":132,"name":"パシフィコ横浜：サマークイーンカップ練習場所","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","image":"/images/points/11180/ko2dmcaoc_1716451383011.jpg","ep":21,"s":173,"mark":"21話：あいらとりずむがみおん様の指導のもと練習していた場所。43話のアクアリウムカップ終了後、りずむがかのんからピュアホワイトウエディングのストーンを受け取った場所でもあります。","density":222,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.45816%2C139.636196"},{"id":"ko2dmcamr","geo":[35.459974,139.635347],"priority":22,"name":"パシフィコ横浜：サマークイーンカップ会場","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"20,21話での激闘の場。43話のアクアリウムカップの会場にもなっています。","density":222,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.459974%2C139.635347"},{"id":"ko2dmcak4","geo":[35.4605,139.637905],"priority":31,"name":"臨港パーク","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"21話：せれのんに負けた3人を見守るJUNさん。「簡単に見つかるオアシスは蜃気楼。熱せられた砂を掘り、指先の痛みを耐えて見つけた湧き水だからこそ、魂を潤し止まりかけたキャラバンの背中を押した。やがて君たちは星に導かれ、真のスタァとして漆黒の闇に光を放つことを……俺は約束する」","density":32,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.4605%2C139.637905"},{"id":"ko2dmcaow","geo":[35.460215,139.637916],"priority":3,"name":"臨港パーク：ダンスバトルだ！","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"43話：アクアリウムカップの激闘の裏で、みおん様とセレナがダンスバトル！","density":32,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.460215%2C139.637916"},{"id":"ko2dmcabh","geo":[35.460499,139.637618],"priority":45,"name":"臨港パーク：夏祭り会場","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"18話：3つのカップルに分かれて会場をぶらぶら。実際に8月に開催されてます。花火は残念ながら2017以降は中止となりました。","density":32,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.460499%2C139.637618"},{"id":"ko2dmcaty","geo":[35.462027,139.638203],"priority":11,"name":"臨港パーク：夏祭りの橋","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"18話：あいらとショウさんがお祭りの時に渡った橋。34話でショウさんとナナの関係に心揺れるあいらが佇んでいたのは、実はこの思い出の場所なのでした…","density":173,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.462027%2C139.638203"},{"id":"ko2dmcaw7","geo":[35.458238,139.632047],"priority":121,"name":"みなとみらい線：地下鉄駅","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"2話：あいらとりずむががプリティートップへ行く時に使った乗った駅？みなとみらい駅ではなく他の駅の可能性もあり","density":374,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.458238%2C139.632047"},{"id":"ko2dmcab2","geo":[35.454993,139.631154],"priority":21,"name":"ランドマークプラザ：プリズムショーのリンク","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"1話他：プリティーシリーズの原点です。ランドマークプラザ（室内）の1階。周りがぐるっとショップに囲まれています。かつては4階にプリズムストーンショップがありました（2018年一時的に復活）。「あいら、服の声を聞くんだっ！」","density":200,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.454993%2C139.631154"},{"id":"ko2dmcaeb","geo":[35.453319,139.63182],"priority":54,"name":"日本丸：誓いの場所","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"25話：あいら、りずむ、みおん様の誓いの場所。その誓いは儚いものとなる予感に胸が締め付けられる…","density":200,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.453319%2C139.63182"},{"id":"ko2dmcato","geo":[35.4527,139.633618],"priority":51,"name":"汽車道：最終回","isFolder":false,"folder":"プリティーリズム","mid":"1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA","s":"","mark":"51話：あいらとショウさんが2人で歩いていた橋","density":211,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1np61pFWxkTJRqf9kc_oTxVruidKiwOA&ll=35.4527%2C139.633618"}]}